{"tid":1813570,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[急] 結婚要擺酒，認真，20萬生意額唔想益藍店，說好的黃色經濟圈呢？","createTime":"2020-01-06T11:16:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T03:24:31.000Z","uid":298259,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"45d1bf151d9bea97a644a0726345ab14c3166090","tid":1813570,"uid":298259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T11:16:37.000Z","msg":"其實本身係落左訂比彩福，但聽聞彩福係藍，上網搵到又話佢中立.....老老實實，戈到20 萬生意，真係唔想博。比左既訂可以退，但擺酒不得不擺......仲要係20圍或以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求求大家比建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 彩福係中立，照擺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 雖然ClubOne 無表態，但佢CEO 係大家樂個仔陳浩弘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點呀點呀？可唔可以擺呀😭😭😭<br />\n<br />\n3. 有人話誠哥其下既酒店....酒店都有點貴，有冇推介<br />\n<br />\n4. 其他<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實，有人開黃既婚宴同酒樓，一定賺到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跪求大家認真建議，呢個係我地黃色經濟圈既一個重大收入，現在同將來都走唔甩，點懲罰黃店都唔及戈一日生意額呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5249e6fe78a95408d2e14e781180f3975e3ced17","tid":1813570,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score